{"tid":1066715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"78歲嬤遭拖禪房性侵　淫僧完事還說「謝謝」","createTime":"2019-03-18T05:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T08:20:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1ee8604a6f3d672da3a4d9f96802d3bad06f2f3a","tid":1066715,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"泰國喀比府一名78歲老婦，日前到家附近一間寺廟採水果時，遭一名年約40歲的僧侶持刀挾持，不料竟遭對方性侵，僧侶得逞後更對她說「謝謝」便揚長而去。心有不甘的老婦隨即到醫院檢查並報案，警方正追捕涉案淫僧。<br />\n泰國《matichon》報導，老婦家離該寺廟僅400多公尺，淫僧當日持刀將她逼入寺內一間禪房，隨即飽嘗獸慾得逞，完事後更向老婦「道謝」態度囂張，隨即揚長而去。又慌又怒的老婦，立即勇敢地到醫院檢查，並在丈夫陪同下報案。<br />\n警方調查後發現，淫僧在數十天前搬到寺廟，沒有人知道他的姓名與身份。警方趕往現場後發現早已人去樓空，禪房內甚至只剩一個枕頭掉在地上。警方打算傳召其他證人，以追蹤該名僧侶的行蹤與背景。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190318/640_1e42446bd146ebbe68acb2a7cbbf5417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190318%2F640_1e42446bd146ebbe68acb2a7cbbf5417.jpg&h=8aad5f82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f8086ee41813e5f58a4936f2f65adb32308a5fc","tid":1066715,"uid":112393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:16:14.000Z","msg":"驅風煲老藕嗒得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806ece2dde8a5e2b893ce738c199bceb4e0a6520","tid":1066715,"uid":1485,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"關節酸痛咪玩咁癲"},{"pid":"f280d7c19d594419a7d99d7ff09c24c4472372aa","tid":1066715,"uid":199162,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"幅圖做乜鳩..."},{"pid":"5388db441c6e6ccc441b0ecdf0132e96dc0f56b4","tid":1066715,"uid":143499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f280d7c19d594419a7d99d7ff09c24c4472372aa","tid":1066715,"uid":199162,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"幅圖做乜鳩..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:11:53.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報啲圖真係精髓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj